master\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/58ebec09453ff578973d88d53240b085?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/58ebec09453ff578973d88d53240b085?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/digitalmaster\" class=\"reviewer-name\">digitalmaster</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 26, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Did not work. Installed, tested, still able to pull up non-secure version of website.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">nothing</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/akmiecik\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f5886ec830dc77c755be6785dec19c7b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f5886ec830dc77c755be6785dec19c7b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/akmiecik\" class=\"reviewer-name\">akmiecik</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 26, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Either they are bad at math (\"one click\") or it does not work.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Well done</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/motorbelly\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/669ebaf59bf64f7fefff1e7d44d8ce7f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/669ebaf59bf64f7fefff1e7d44d8ce7f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/motorbelly\" class=\"reviewer-name\"> <small>(motorbelly)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 3, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Love simplicity</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Easy setup</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/maryleemac\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/91b35ccd3df0126afa19b8de255eb3e0?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/91b35ccd3df0126afa19b8de255eb3e0?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/maryleemac\" class=\"reviewer-name\">maryleemac</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">October 24, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I had to change one thing and that was to change my site from <code>http://</code> to <code>https://</code>. Once I did that, the plugin worked perfectly. Thanks for a great plugin.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Easy, light, fast and simple!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/developit\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/99db410ef8a438c67f56c30a95f2c67e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/99db410ef8a438c67f56c30a95f2c67e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/developit\" class=\"reviewer-name\">developit</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">October 24, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Excellent plugin! The only one that offers HSTS for FREE!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Awesome Plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/arsalanmehmood\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9c0f9b74732833486785329567b06e1d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9c0f9b74732833486785329567b06e1d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/arsalanmehmood\" class=\"reviewer-name\">arsalanmehmood</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">October 22, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Thanks for saving my day. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Bravo, chicos.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/espasiko\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/018dd843d5e6a28426c51af5c803148c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/018dd843d5e6a28426c51af5c803148c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/espasiko\" class=\"reviewer-name\">espasiko</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">October 20, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Bravo, chicos.</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:103:\"Enable SSL with 1 click! Add an SSL certificate &amp; WP Force SSL to redirect site from HTTP to HTTPS.\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:59:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/wp-force-ssl.1.5.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:2:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/wp-force-ssl/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=2160904\";s:7:\"caption\";s:63:\"After activation, all traffic is redirected from HTTP to HTTPS.\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/wp-force-ssl/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=2160904\";s:7:\"caption\";s:49:\"Test your SSL certificate with our built-in tool.\";}}s:4:\"tags\";a:5:{s:7:\"add-ssl\";s:7:\"add ssl\";s:10:\"enable-ssl\";s:10:\"enable ssl\";s:9:\"force-ssl\";s:9:\"force ssl\";s:5:\"https\";s:5:\"https\";s:3:\"ssl\";s:3:\"ssl\";}s:8:\"versions\";a:3:{s:3:\"1.4\";s:59:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/wp-force-ssl.1.4.zip\";s:3:\"1.5\";s:59:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/wp-force-ssl.1.5.zip\";s:5:\"trunk\";s:55:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/wp-force-ssl.zip\";}s:11:\"donate_link\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"banners\";a:2:{s:3:\"low\";s:67:\"https://ps.w.org/wp-force-ssl/assets/banner-772x250.jpg?rev=1593573\";s:4:\"high\";